hat i mean that you will summon on and it will be green to you. At which point you will destroy it and resummon until you get a blue pet =) .. makes a LOT of difference.<br><br> For my attacks / hunts .. i usually park my pet (/pet guard here) than go find a mob .. cast darkness to get his attention and run back to fluffy.  If its a LONG pull i will stop part way to add a dot. Than ... send pet fear and redot / dark .. and wait for it to drop =)<br><br> Your attack styles will change a lot at different times =) .. when you get shock of posion .. you will start nuking to death instead of dotting .. it becomes a lot easier than .. and when you get root .. wow .. entirely different game =)<br><br> One of the things i really enjoy each spell lvl .. is the new pet .. its just really fun. the last 2 lvls leading up to new spells are usually harder, you are having to hunt harder mobs for the same xp, and poor fluffy isnt getting a increase in power. Sooo, we we do get a new pet / spells its like a kid in a candy store ... just LOTS of fun =)<br><br> hehehehe ... need less to say .. i LOVE necros<br> <p><hr><center><font color=navy><center><b><font face="Arial" size=+2>Askyn</font></b></center><font face="Arial" size=-1 >Level 46 Iksar Necromancer<br><font color=red>Don't fear death. You will make a nice PET …</font><br></font></font><font face="Arial" size=-2><font color="#3E3EFF">T</font><font color="#3E3EFF">h</font><font color="#3E3EFF">e</font><font color="#3E3EFF"> </font><font color="#3E3EFF">H</font><font color="#3E3EFF">u</font><font color="#3E3EFF">n</font><font color="#3E3EFF">t</font><font color="#3E3EFF">s</font><font color="#3E3EFF">m</font><font color="#3E3EFF">a</font><font color="#3E3EFF">n</font><font color="#3E3EFF"> </font><font color="#3E3EFF">f</font><font color="#3E3EFF">o</font><font color="#3E3EFF">r</font></font> <a href="http:www.eqrandomacts.com"> <b><font face="Arial" size=-1><font color="#808080">R</font><font color="#8B8B8B">a<